${voffset 5}${color1}Name${goto 180}CPU%${alignr}MEM%
${color2}${top name 1} ${goto 180}${top cpu 1}${alignr}${top mem 1}${color3}
${top name 2} ${goto 180}${top cpu 2}${alignr}${top mem 2}
